Hello! Welcome to Elite's Universe, here this is a discord server for Elite's fan as he streams, uploads and chats to viewers!
As you may know, there are rules to be read, we suggest reading them just so you don't get falsed warned :D

__**General Rules:**__
Rule 1: No NSFW in any form, there is no NSFW coming to this server at all, if this is posted to a channel. You will be permanently banned, appeals are available as always, but for 30 days only
Rule 2: We like to keep it family friendly here, so no swearing at all, this will vary between what you say and who you say it to
Rule 3: We take any form of abuse like cyber abuse in words or saying "I will kill you" in dms or on the server, note that if it is in dms, we need proof or we cannot punish them
Rule 4: We don't want any daters like people meeting for the first time and talking a lot and getting in the way of others, if you like someone and you want to talk about a lot, please move to dms
Rule 5: Use all channels correctly, if you do it on accident or the do this the first time, we understand. Mistakes are mistakes!
Rule 6: We don't take any people bringing people down like, Billy is gonna run a marathon, and Bob tells him that he is bad at running and Billy doesn't do the marathon now
Rule 7: Don't overuse bots or just hog it to you, other people want to see their stats as well!
Rule 8: Racism is not permitted anywhere in this servr at all! If you are racist, you'll be permanently banned without an appeal
Rule 9: Don't spam, just don't be **THAT** guy, come on please

__**Note:**__ In some channels, some other rules are added just for your safety!

**-Member Roles-**

Verified - Default Member role.
Can invite people to server and change nickname.

Twitch Regular - Active twitch viewer on Elite's streams.

Partner - Server partners shown in #partnership.
Can talk in #partnership in addition to all Verified perms.

Gamer to Elite Gamer - Leveling roles.  Gain no other special perms.

Twitch VIP - VIP on Elite's streams.
Access to VIP channel.

Twitch Sub - Sub on Elite's streams.
Access to VIP and Sub channels.

Twitch Mod - Mod on Elite's streams.
Access to VIP channel.

**-- Staff roles --**

Trial Moderator - Moderators who got accepted and are on their trial period for moderating on this server.
Mod - Moderators who have been trusted and have hit the moderator stage.
Head Mod - Moderators who have been on the team for a while and are trusted.

Admin - Moderators who have applied for administrator are the higher-ups in the server.

Head Admin - Administrators who have been on the admin team for a while and are trusted.

Co-Owner: In addition to Elite, the owner of the server, we have Co-Owner which is the second owner of the server.

Elite (Owner): This is a private role to only the owner of the server, Elite.
